subject: Xlib/XCB: passing the error in xreply to the extension who sent the request.
commitMessage:
Xlib/XCB: passing the error in xreply to the extension who sent the request.

   The error in x-reply is the result of x client's request of one
   of the extensions. In this case, the error must be handled by
   the extension who sent the request.

Change-Id: I5621d637ca41361b7dfab9910a52951fec47f093
Signed-off-by: Boram Park <boram1288.park@samsung.com>

subject: libX11 should not try to build into a pure wayland platform..
commitMessage:
libX11 should not try to build into a pure wayland platform..

This package is designed for an X server platform.

In a system released, based exclusively on Wayland platform, it should be in a excluded status.

Tizen devel  | Tizen release
_____________|______________
succeeded    | succeeded
excluded     | excluded
broken       |
failed       |
unresolvable |
blocked      |
locked       |
note:
    - The disabled status is only
      allowed for OBS administration

Change-Id: I8435d15c37d26f913c457bf6e55cc71acae648ad
Signed-off-by: Ronan Le Martret <ronan@fridu.net>
